Sentencas: We have developed high-performance oxygen electrodes for reversible solid oxide cells.
Titulo: Further improvement in performances of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ - doped ceria composite oxygen electrodes with infiltrated doped ceria nanoparticles for reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) center dot (CeO2)(0.8)(SmO1.5)(0.2) (SDC) composite scaffolds were infiltrated with SDC nanoparticles.
Titulo: Further improvement in performances of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ - doped ceria composite oxygen electrodes with infiltrated doped ceria nanoparticles for reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The electrode with 30 vol% load of SDC nanoparticles exhibited very low overpotentials, eta <= 0.010 V for anodic and vertical bar eta vertical bar <= 0.030 V for cathodic reactions at 0.7 A cm(-2) and 800 degrees C, which was ascribed to a noticeable increase in the exchange current densities.
Titulo: Further improvement in performances of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ - doped ceria composite oxygen electrodes with infiltrated doped ceria nanoparticles for reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The electrodes have shown very stable performance under anodic oxygen evolution operation at -0.5 A cm(-2) and 750 degrees C for 400 h. Such electrodes developed are extremely promising oxygen electrodes for R-SOC ever reported.
Titulo: Further improvement in performances of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ - doped ceria composite oxygen electrodes with infiltrated doped ceria nanoparticles for reversible solid oxide cells
